{"type": "article", "id": 6097, "title": "Cosmo 沙发", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-11T07:17:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143631Yzg19TSWKVi2JkbR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t巴伦西亚家具品牌 Missana 日前发布了一款名为「Cosmo」的沙发，由 La Selva 设计工作室的设计师 David Galvañ Y Manuel Bañó 操刀设计。设计师在设计过程中充分考虑了人坐下去的舒适度，赋予了它一个适当的弧度，并且搭配了优质的裹面材料，以求在温暖与功能性之间找到一个最恰当的平衡点。此外，David Galvañ Y Manuel Bañó 还为 Cosmo 的一侧配置了一个小型支架，用户可以随手放置一些杂物。提供蓝、黑与红 3 种配色。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143629SUufqngmdj8HbiQP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061436292bYxGUNoT9SI8wpC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143630gx8YBFvQ4Uycnrbw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143630oPhugDd95tG0sH8C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}